{"tid":1174743,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"金屬究竟有冇味?","createTime":"2019-05-28T05:19:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T15:54:17.000Z","uid":136590,"like":42,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cfbdbe9a8d007a872325b8d16ca81fe8fc3dccdc","tid":1174743,"uid":136590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T05:19:08.000Z","msg":"相信大家睇完個topic 第一個反應就係「呢條係咩問題嚟? 開post條友係咪on9?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n金屬當然係有味 我相信大部份人都會認同<br />\n如果你依家拎起個$1 捽兩捽 然後聞下個$1或者自己隻手<br />\n你一定會聞到一種獨特嘅金屬味 (俗啲講就係銅臭味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n其實唔單止硬幣 平時當你摸完其他金屬之後 (e.g.開門摸完門柄)<br />\n其實你都會聞到類似嘅氣味 我諗大家都經歷過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係<br />\n如果你諗真啲嘅話 其實成件事好似唔係幾make sense<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為一樣物件要有氣味 最起碼要符合以下兩個條件<br />\n1.) 呢樣物件要足夠地volatile (i.e. 佢或多或少都要釋放一啲vapour)<br />\n2.) 呢樣物件唔可以係odourless (我知呢個condition真係好撚廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n咁點解最起碼要符合呢兩個條件先「有可能」有氣味?<br />\n首先當我地聞到一樣物件嘅氣味<br />\n其實我地只係聞緊佢釋放出嚟嘅gas/vapour<br />\n呢啲氣體經空氣走到入我地個鼻裡面 所以我地先會聞到有味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一個條件就係確保「釋放氣體」呢點成立<br />\n而其實好多液體同固體或多或少都會釋放一啲vapour<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (當然釋放嘅速度一定唔同)<br />\n當中液體通常都會比固體釋出更多vapour (mainly depends on the strength of interactions between molecules)<br />\n咁亦都解釋到 點解多數液體都會有佢地獨特嘅氣味<br />\n但係固體就明顯比較少有 (Organic compound除外)<br />\n第二個條件就唔洗解釋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n絕大部份嘅金屬喺室溫正正就係唔符合呢兩個主要條件<br />\n大家中學讀chem都學過 金屬入面嘅atoms係held by metallic bond<br />\n呢種bonding對比起普通liquid入面嘅interactions要強得多<br />\n所以大部份嘅金屬喺室溫幾乎係唔會release任何vapour<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再加上本身已經係odourless 就算真係有vapour我地都唔會用個鼻detect到<br />\n當然都有少數例外 其中一個就係水銀<br />\n因為佢喺室溫已經係液體 所以會持續釋放vapour<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而呢個亦都係水銀點解咁危險嘅原因之一 (剩係啲vapour已經毒撚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n既然金屬理論上應該係冇味<br />\n咁我地平時究竟聞緊啲乜撚嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最近nilered正正就住呢個topic出咗條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(p.s. NileRed同NurdRage都係非常高質嘅youtube chemist<br />\n對chem有興趣嘅可以睇下佢地嘅片)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BqLH-nTZEOc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBqLH-nTZEOc&d=4a077UaaKOqSfaiyS2iiQc5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=594d0a5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BqLH-nTZEOc</a><br />\n<br />\n喺度落返個credit先<br />\n其實我主要都係轉述條片講過嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n純粹係share啲有趣topic等大家知道chemistry有趣嘅一面<br />\n<br />\n好啦咁到底金屬啲味喺嚟自邊度?<br />\n其實就係嚟自你自己隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每個人對手上面其實都有好多油脂同手汗<br />\n當我地隻手掂到金屬表面 (e.g. iron, copper, zinc)<br />\n呢啲金屬就會變成catalyst去催化一啲化學反應<br />\n呢啲反應會將我地手上嘅油份氧化做其他有氣味嘅molecules<br />\n而其中最主要嘅product就係 1-octen-3-one (其實我都唔知係乜嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n換句話講 其實我地平時所講嘅「銅臭味」<br />\n主要就係嚟自1-octen-3-one 而唔係金屬本身<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要驗證呢個講法啱唔啱其實都好簡單<br />\n我地只要戴手套 仔細洗乾淨一個$1硬幣<br />\n依家你應該係聞唔到嗰陣熟悉嘅金屬味 (但係你應該會聞到番梘味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n如果你再用手捽兩捽 陣銅臭味應該就會返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於點樣整1-octen-3-one 大家就要睇上面條片<br />\n(小弟唔係讀chem出身 格硬講盞俾人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n最尾根據NileRed嘅講法 dilute嘅1-octen-3-one的確非常似我地平時聞慣嘅金屬味<br />\n各位連登chemist有興趣都可以自己試下整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n整完仲可以搽落啲九唔搭八嘅嘢度去整蠱人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等佢地聞到個腦死機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1791834be491b52b303056d69b6dd42958d3f0be","tid":1174743,"uid":61882,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T05:44:50.000Z","msg":"滿身銅臭既人<br />\n臭既只係自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11b412a5c60ab429426e9b2dcd14f2a6199b39b5","tid":1174743,"uid":75139,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T07:28:00.000Z","msg":"鬼唔知咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇手汗個陣冇味<br />\n有手汗個陣有味"},{"pid":"38f641f32b019c60bcfd13834834538b5aa1d383","tid":1174743,"uid":112551,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T07:58:31.000Z","msg":"同食餅有餅味差唔多道理"},{"pid":"482f323a209a512ff3e5e4d6b1102f30041160b8","tid":1174743,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T11:17:13.000Z","msg":"反而想知道鹽鹹嘅原因係乜 係因為Na+ 定Cl- 中學老師話係Cl- 但wiki 話係Na+"},{"pid":"cc886802524c9b202afd792a569dbf546d6b14ec","tid":1174743,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T11:17:34.000Z","msg":"鐵有鐵味可能係因為Fe3+ 同血嘅味差唔多"},{"pid":"aa3dcf2f082d8ce25ab93535494de962f856b52a","tid":1174743,"uid":26711,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"11b412a5c60ab429426e9b2dcd14f2a6199b39b5","tid":1174743,"uid":75139,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T07:28:00.000Z","msg":"鬼唔知咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇手汗個陣冇味<br />\n有手汗個陣有味"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T11:19:41.000Z","msg":"叻唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f13e742893df76ccf71bf918c0665fff8eac6cfc","tid":1174743,"uid":136590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"482f323a209a512ff3e5e4d6b1102f30041160b8","tid":1174743,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T11:17:13.000Z","msg":"反而想知道鹽鹹嘅原因係乜 係因為Na+ 定Cl- 中學老師話係Cl- 但wiki 話係Na+"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T11:51:05.000Z","msg":"我諗Na+應該機會比較大<br />\n依稀記得人嘅脷有啲sodium channel可以俾Na+入去<br />\n不過味覺我就真係唔sure 有冇bio高手解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c3a6b7da3963701e5e4c93cd3902de31677f9f9","tid":1174743,"uid":178205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T11:54:28.000Z","msg":"我以為係金屬本身表面癡咗野 (油污垢)<br />\n你捽翻出嚟<br />\n或者有少少氧化咗 好脆弱 你捽就甩咁"},{"pid":"b23d6b68eda829fdb4c5f0413b61830ee7f34215","tid":1174743,"uid":109416,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T12:07:59.000Z","msg":"可樂 用鋁罐同玻璃裝都唔同味 你話呢"},{"pid":"7acfce1005244d3c6a9f7053b7b30db0266eb8f4","tid":1174743,"uid":85439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T12:08:43.000Z","msg":"睇兩眼已經知講緊NileRed條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48ce6c482426ed61f1128a3651bf43984ac014ea","tid":1174743,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T12:09:18.000Z","msg":"奶過<br />\n好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4272364776a0c9f65b9fd04cdc38209dd1ab1757","tid":1174743,"uid":136590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c3a6b7da3963701e5e4c93cd3902de31677f9f9","tid":1174743,"uid":178205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T11:54:28.000Z","msg":"我以為係金屬本身表面癡咗野 (油污垢)<br />\n你捽翻出嚟<br />\n或者有少少氧化咗 好脆弱 你捽就甩咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T12:16:06.000Z","msg":"我地最尾聞到嘅銅臭味應該都係混雜埋呢啲嘢嘅味<br />\n只係1-octen-3-one係當中最強烈最有代表性嘅"},{"pid":"7e21449baef87e1ff259d8e5a0ca529673431def","tid":1174743,"uid":136590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7acfce1005244d3c6a9f7053b7b30db0266eb8f4","tid":1174743,"uid":